My take after watching this sparing:
Gibs, footwork, shot selection and defence are a bit poor in my eyes compared to Jake.... jake Paul is the better all around boxer by a long shot... that being said gibs pressure along with cardio will be his key factors coming into the fight... jake is also the much bigger man and carries more power.... the only way I see gib wining this is by outworking jake with cardio and constant pressure. I do believe jake Paul has this win.
